## Audit Findings
- The hero section was not clear for first-time users
- Navigation felt confusing and not focused
- No clear call-to-action for users
- Information hierarchy was not strong

## What I Focused On
- Simplified navigation for better clarity
- Designed a strong hero section with clear messaging
- Added product cards for easy understanding

## What I Would Do Next
- Add testimonials and trust signals
- Improve UI design with better spacing and colors
- Make the website fully responsive for mobile